ygData.messageBody:
Hehe - oh yeah - forgot to mention that I am wearing steel boots, legs and
breast plate now (looks are everything!) along with bone plate arms, purity
belt, polar bear cloak, dark elf hide gloves, the top knot hat, and some
very nice jewel craft bracers, rings, earrings, silver ruby veil & golden
black pearl choker (I'll get exact names and stats of rings, etc, only one I
remember for sure is golden amber earrings - I think)

Sylly Songsynger
Bard of the 24th song
Selling Swords and Such
somewhere on Innoruuk

p.s. I killed _A LOT_ of wisps!!! (hehe)

p.s.s. fighting hard to be _the_ most twinked bard on Innoruuk I am the
first to admit it!
